		<note>
			<para>By using the monitor function, enabled from the 
				<keycap>&#x25b2;<alt>up</alt></keycap>
				or
				<keycap>&#x25bc;<alt>down</alt></keycap>
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
